    "description": "<strong>我们希望有更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是团队的最大动力！感谢！<br>《文明守护者：抗争》交流QQ群：836724589</strong><br><br><strong>《文明守护者》是一款原创的防守型4X策略类游戏。在游戏中，你将扮演文明的领袖，通过选择适当特性、利用资源发展科技、为人民规划目标并逐步建设成为更庞大的城市。在这过程中，你还将养成独属于文明的英雄，在贪婪的敌人如潮水般不断入侵中坚守住自己的城市，带领文明迈向更辉煌的未来。相信当你利用自己精心选择的策略度过每一场以少胜多时的过程，都将带给你最独特的游戏体验。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/3a512d92bf81c1490c6403bc1287e788.webp?t=1737097264\" width=615 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2058d10c318482dfad6b2c3c15866740.poster.avif?t=1737097264\" width=614 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2058d10c318482dfad6b2c3c15866740.webm?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2058d10c318482dfad6b2c3c15866740.mp4?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每次游玩都将生成独一无二的世界，从风格各异的文明特性中选择本局的发展方向，并任用不同领域的英雄人物助力文明的发展，让你的每一局游戏都有新的体验。 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/98870e0eabda2b72244b512c92fc4876.webp?t=1737097264\" width=615 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/158460e045f6c819ee1795c063268972.poster.avif?t=1737097264\" width=614 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/158460e045f6c819ee1795c063268972.webm?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/158460e045f6c819ee1795c063268972.mp4?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>你将在战役模式中亲历哪些历史上的著名守卫战争，作为指挥官利用有限的资源抵御数量庞大的敌人，利用你的谋略超越古代将领，获得战斗的胜利！（该玩法将持续更新。）</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/43f1de2d9071beee42e534cb106c2c64.webp?t=1737097264\" width=615 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/538136c09e21db462530e923964b7786.poster.avif?t=1737097264\" width=614 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/538136c09e21db462530e923964b7786.webm?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/538136c09e21db462530e923964b7786.mp4?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>将各种各样的英雄招募麾下，让他们随文明共同成长。更有独属于这个时代的限定英雄，协助你抵御外敌，成就伟业！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/34fedd1a1850f0a35c50c3f363416224.webp?t=1737097264\" width=615 height=56 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2a17ee9570a06c555a537ee3ff8ec2ea.poster.avif?t=1737097264\" width=614 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2a17ee9570a06c555a537ee3ff8ec2ea.webm?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183500/extras/2a17ee9570a06c555a537ee3ff8ec2ea.mp4?t=1737097264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>新生的文明总要面对时代的考验，更何况这是个强敌环伺的世界。你将在危机之下寻找发展的道路，努力从八批强大的攻击中守护住自己的文明。更有多种难度，完成不断攀升的挑战吧！</strong>",
